---
---
<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
  <img
    class="hero-bg"
    src="/images/hero-meadow.webp"
    alt="A native meadow in golden afternoon light"
    width="2400"
    height="1600"
    fetchpriority="high"
    loading="eager"
  />
  <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="hero-content container">
    <p class="hero-label">A DOCUMENTARY FILM &middot; 2026</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title" id="hero-title">The World's Best Office</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      A thirteen-acre estate in Greenwich, Connecticut shows what happens when elite
      landscape architecture meets native ecology. In Minnesota, 42,000 homeowners
      applied to replace their lawns with native meadow. In Pennsylvania, the same
      program was oversubscribed by 300 percent. This is the story of the most
      resource-intensive landscape in America &mdash; and what comes back when we let it go.
    </p>
    <a href="#founding-partner" class="btn btn-primary btn-hero">
      Become a Founding Partner
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    min-height: 100vh; /* fallback */
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    /* Placeholder gradient — replaced when real photography is swapped in */
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      #0f1f0f 0%,
      #1e3a1e 30%,
      #2d4f2d 55%,
      #3a6335 80%,
      #2a4a28 100%
    );
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* Semi-transparent overlay ensures text contrast against any photo */
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(28, 43, 30, 0.55);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: var(--space-24);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--color-straw);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #F7F3EC;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #F7F3EC;
    max-width: 52ch;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    opacity: 0.92;
  }

  .btn-hero {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-12);
    min-height: 52px;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }

    .btn-hero {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
    }
  }
</style>
